    <item>
      <title>FTX 债权人有望提振陷入困境的加密货币市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ftx-creditors-may-boost-struggling-bitcoin-btc-crypto-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币交易所 FTX 的债权人将在未来几个月根据法院批准的支付计划获得超过 120 亿美元的资金，这增加了部分现金可能重新投入数字资产的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/ftx-creditors-may-boost-struggling-bitcoin-btc-crypto-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度警告影子银行若不能控制风险将采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/india-warns-shadow-banks-of-action-if-they-fail-to-curtail-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行警告影子银行建立强有力的风险缓解系统，例如以更全面的方式评估个人借款人的信用价值，否则央行可能不得不介入并采取监管行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/india-warns-shadow-banks-of-action-if-they-fail-to-curtail-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 06:49:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>力拓集团押注锂业，完成 2007 年以来最大交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/rio-wins-approval-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-for-6-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团已同意以全现金方式收购 Arcadium Lithium Plc，对这家美国矿业公司的估值为 67 亿美元，此举将扩大其对电池金属的控制力，并凭借 17 年来最大的一笔交易重返并购领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/rio-wins-approval-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-for-6-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 05:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
